title: Lab Portal - PharmEasy Labs
description:
Note: This app is intended for the use of registered partners only.

Lab Portal is the storefront partner app used by PharmEasy Lab partners (franchises) to punch in diagnostic orders, download reports, manage customer lifecycle, identify details of various diagnostic tests, and much more. Armed with this app, franchise partners can now grow their revenues and businesses further by harnessing the benefits of its cutting-edge technology.

Want to take up a diagnostic franchise with Pharmeasy Labs? Write to us at: labsfranchise@pharmeasy.in
